<TestCaseEntity>
   <description>When a user tap/clicks on the collapsed  Details drawer (at the bottom of the offer card)

Then the system shall:

Expand the Offer-Details to display in the offer-card
The Offer-Card-Details will be scrollable when legal copy extends past offer-card boundary
Details_Title 
if unconsolidated
Lease/Finance: {offerType ON} &lt;year>&lt;model>&lt;trim>&lt;drivetrain> &lt;pacakges>
Cash: &quot;{offerType BACK ON}  &lt;year>&lt;model>&lt;trim>&lt;drivetrain> &lt;pacakges>
College Grad/Military: &quot;{offerType REBATE ON}  &lt;year>&lt;model>&lt;trim>&lt;drivetrain> &lt;packages>
if consolidated:
Lease/Finance: &lt;offerType> ON SELECT &lt;year>&lt;model>&lt;trim>&lt;drivetrain> &lt;pacakges> STYLES
Cash: &quot;&lt;offerType> BACK ON  SELECT &lt;year>&lt;model>&lt;trim>&lt;drivetrain> &lt;pacakges> STYLES
College Grad/Military: &quot;&lt;offerType> REBATE ON SELECT &lt;year>&lt;model>&lt;trim>&lt;drivetrain> &lt;pacakges> STYLES
Detail-Trims
Should come from both LOD and AEM
Will only appear on consolidated Offer-card
Select styles: &lt;year>&lt;model>&lt;trim>&lt;drivetrain> , ...
comma delimited between each Model-trim
Legal-Copy appear as defined in LOD</description>
